Occurrence records for the species Parides gundlachianus

Source: R/data_documentation.R
sp_occurrences.Rd

Dataset containing geographic coordinates of a Cuban butterfly.

sp_occurrences

Format

A data.frame with 19 rows and 3 columns.

name

character, species scientific name.

longitude

numeric, longitude values.

latitude

numeric, latitude values.

Source

https://www.gbif.org/

Examples

data("sp_occurrences", package = "biosurvey")
head(sp_occurrences)

#>                    name longitude latitude
#> 1 Parides gundlachianus -75.67899 19.93802
#> 2 Parides gundlachianus -76.75754 19.96988
#> 3 Parides gundlachianus -75.77580 19.96306
#> 4 Parides gundlachianus -75.16496 19.91625
#> 5 Parides gundlachianus -75.11273 19.92760
#> 6 Parides gundlachianus -74.47480 20.30393
